---
---

<div class="grid gap-12">
  <!-- Vintago Project -->
  <article class="project-card relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200/70 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/90 to-slate-50/90 dark:from-slate-950/90 dark:to-slate-900/90 p-8 shadow-2xl shadow-slate-900/10 dark:shadow-black/20 backdrop-blur-xl">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 font-semibold">Proyecto Estratégico</p>
          <h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Vintago</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">E-commerce & Branding</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          Marca de streetwear propia. Frontend desacoplado construido en <span class="font-semibold">Astro + React</span>, con animaciones scroll-based en <span class="font-semibold">GSAP (ScrollTrigger)</span>. El backend es <span class="font-semibold">WooCommerce como headless commerce</span>: el frontend consume la <span class="font-semibold">Store API REST de WooCommerce</span> para catálogo, carrito y checkout, con <span class="font-semibold">autenticación JWT</span> para login de usuarios. Personalicé el backend con <span class="font-semibold">snippets vía WPCode</span> (CORS entre subdominios, tema oscuro del checkout, integración del login JWT).
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 pt-4">
          <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold">Astro</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-400 text-sm font-semibold">React</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-pink-100 dark:bg-pink-900/30 text-pink-700 dark:text-pink-400 text-sm font-semibold">GSAP</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 text-sm font-semibold">WooCommerce (Headless)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-4">
          <a href="https://vintago.com.co/" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 font-semibold hover:gap-3 transition-all">
            Visitar Vintago →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[1.5rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-100 to-slate-200 dark:from-slate-800 dark:to-slate-700 h-96 shadow-lg">
        <img src="/vintago.jpg" alt="Vintago streetwear project" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/10 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- Dotaciones JR Project -->
  <article class="project-card relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200/70 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/90 to-slate-50/90 dark:from-slate-950/90 dark:to-slate-900/90 p-8 shadow-2xl shadow-slate-900/10 dark:shadow-black/20 backdrop-blur-xl">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 font-semibold">En Desarrollo ⚠️</p>
          <h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Dotaciones JR</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">CRM con Facturación Electrónica DIAN</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          CRM para gestión de dotaciones: inventario, clientes, proveedores, gastos e ingresos, con <span class="font-semibold">facturación electrónica integrada a la DIAN</span>. Backend en <span class="font-semibold">Laravel (API REST)</span> y <span class="font-semibold">MySQL</span>, integrando el proveedor tecnológico <span class="font-semibold">Factus</span> para la validación de facturas ante la DIAN (CUFE, XML, PDF).
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 pt-4">
          <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-green-700 dark:text-green-400 text-sm font-semibold">Laravel</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold">MySQL</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-400 text-sm font-semibold">DIAN</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900/30 text-orange-700 dark:text-orange-400 text-sm font-semibold">Factus</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[1.5rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-100 to-slate-200 dark:from-slate-800 dark:to-slate-700 h-96 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
        <div class="text-6xl opacity-20">📦</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- Vintago.tech Project -->
  <article class="project-card relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-200/70 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/90 to-slate-50/90 dark:from-slate-950/90 dark:to-slate-900/90 p-8 shadow-2xl shadow-slate-900/10 dark:shadow-black/20 backdrop-blur-xl">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 font-semibold">Catálogo Tecnológico</p>
          <h3 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Vintago.tech</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Catálogo e-commerce tecnológico con enfoque en conversión</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          Catálogo digital de 300+ productos tecnológicos. Construido en <span class="font-semibold">Next.js + Tailwind</span>, desplegado en Netlify, con flujo de conversión directo a WhatsApp optimizado para compra desde móvil.
        </p>
        <div class="grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-3 pt-4">
          <span class="rounded-full bg-indigo-100 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-700 dark:bg-indigo-900/30 dark:text-indigo-400">Experimentación</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-purple-100 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-purple-700 dark:bg-purple-900/30 dark:text-purple-400">Optimización</span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-800 dark:text-slate-300">WhatsApp Commerce</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <span class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Next.js · Tailwind · Netlify · WhatsApp</span>
          <span class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100">Rendimiento</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-4">
          <a href="https://vintago-tech.netlify.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-2xl border border-slate-900 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 transition hover:bg-slate-100 dark:border-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-950 dark:text-white dark:hover:bg-slate-900">
            Ver Vintago.tech
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[1.5rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-100 to-slate-200 dark:from-slate-800 dark:to-slate-700 h-96 shadow-lg">
        <img src="/vintago-tech.png" alt="Vintago.tech catalog project" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-slate-900/10 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</div>

<style is:global>
  :root { --neon-cyan: #00f3ff; --neon-purple: #7c3aed; }
  .project-card { transition: transform 400ms cubic-bezier(.2,.9,.2,1), box-shadow 400ms ease, border-color 300ms ease; position: relative; }
  .project-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; right: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,243,255,0.02), transparent 30%);
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
    opacity: 0.9;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  .project-card > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .project-card:hover { transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.01); border-color: rgba(0,243,255,0.45); box-shadow: 0 40px 120px rgba(0,243,255,0.12), inset 0 0 60px rgba(124,58,237,0.04); }

  /* Neon edge glow stronger in dark mode */
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .project-card::before { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0,243,255,0.05), rgba(124,58,237,0.02)); }
    .project-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 48px 140px rgba(0,243,255,0.18), 0 12px 40px rgba(124,58,237,0.06); border-color: rgba(0,243,255,0.6); }
  }

  /* Scanline sweep */
  .project-card .card-scan {
    position: absolute; left: -40%; top: 0; width: 40%; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), transparent); transform: skewX(-18deg); opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 2;
  }
  .project-card:hover .card-scan { animation: card-scan 900ms cubic-bezier(.2,.9,.2,1); opacity: 1; }
  @keyframes card-scan { 0% { left:-40%; opacity:0 } 20% { opacity:0.9 } 100% { left:140%; opacity:0 } }

  /* Neon icon/background accent inside image block */
  .project-card .accent-emoji { transition: transform 400ms ease, opacity 400ms ease; }
  .project-card:hover .accent-emoji { transform: translateY(-6px) scale(1.06); opacity: 0.95; }

  /* Make badges glow a bit */
  .project-card .px-4.py-2.rounded-full { box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,243,255,0.04) inset; }
  .project-card a { transition: color 200ms ease, gap 200ms ease; }
</style>



